article.description: — Corey Camper Jr.'s 21 points helped UTEP defeat Liberty 67-51 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Camper's 21 lead UTEP past Liberty 67-51
article.story: LYNCHBURG, Va. -- — Corey Camper Jr.'s 21 points helped UTEP defeat Liberty 67-51 on Saturday night. Camper had six rebounds for the Miners (15-15, 6-9 Conference USA). Zid Powell shot 7 of 9 from the field and 4 for 6 from the line to add 19 points. Tae Hardy finished with 12 points. Kaden Metheny led the way for the Flames (17-12, 6-8) with 15 points. Kyle Rode added 13 points and two steals for Liberty. Brody Peebles also had eight points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
